语配音版的做法，但不知道在日本是否会做剧场放映。<\/span><\/p>","vod_play_from":"snm3u8","vod_play_server":"no","vod_play_note":"","vod_play_url":"HD$https:\/\/v14.yuglf.com\/202604\/11\/AGydxQYNaG19\/video\/index.m3u8","vod_down_from":"","vod_down_server":"","vod_down_note":"","vod_down_url":"","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type_name":"动作片"}]}